# api-endpoints

## Meeting Management Endpoints
Importance Score: 85/100

1. Signal Extraction API
- `/api/meetings/{id}/signals`
- Extracts structured business signals from meeting content with custom categorization:
  - Decisions
  - Action Items
  - Blockers
  - Risks
  - Ideas
- Implements automatic signal deduplication and merging
- Links signals to source meeting context

2. Meeting Intelligence Endpoints 
- `/api/meetings/analyze`
- Process meeting transcripts through intelligence pipeline
- Integrates screenshot analysis for visual context
- Maintains temporal relationships between related meetings
- Associates extracted signals with parent meetings

## Document Management Endpoints
