1. Knowledge Graph Integration
- `/api/documents/knowledge`
- Builds semantic relationships between documents
- Implements DIKW pyramid classification:
  - Data level documents
  - Information synthesis
  - Knowledge extraction
  - Wisdom distillation
- Maintains document hierarchies and relationships

2. Document Intelligence
- `/api/documents/analyze`
- Extracts domain-specific insights
- Links related meetings and signals
- Maintains document version relationships
- Generates semantic tags for knowledge organization

